HEADWORD: Main-hamper
<hw>Main"-ham`per</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[F.
<ets>main</ets> hand (see <er>Main</er> a hand at dice) + E.
<ets>hamper</ets>.]</ety> <def>A hamper to be carried in the hand; a
hand basket used in carrying grapes to the press.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

